00:00:00,280 --> 00:00:03,490
Below are some business factors to take into consideration when

2
00:00:03,490 --> 00:00:06,950
deciding whether to buy a software component from a third-party vendor.

3
00:00:06,950 --> 00:00:09,390
For each, determine whether the factor is enhanced or

4
00:00:09,390 --> 00:00:11,300
diminished if you decide to buy.

5
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:13,930
Put a plus next to factors that are benefitted and

6
00:00:13,930 --> 00:00:15,980
a minus next to factors that are diminished.

7
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:18,800
First, your uniqueness with respect to your competitors.

8
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:22,290
Second, the amount of your staff time required to develop the product of which

9
00:00:22,290 --> 00:00:23,510
the component is a part.

10
00:00:23,510 --> 00:00:25,470
Third, your overall production costs.

11
00:00:25,470 --> 00:00:28,210
And fourth, your control of the development process.
